Title: RNA sequencing analysis of SczA-deficient Streptococcus agalactiae during Zn intoxication
Description: Total RNA was isolated from mid-log phase Streptococcus agalactiae cells deficient in SczA (∆sczA strain GU2791), grown in Todd-Hewitt broth (THB) medium supplemented with 0.25 mM Zn and sequenced using Illumina NextSeq500.
